metadata.name: DKTW#148
metadata.description: A collection of 150 NFTs based on the most memorable tweets from the Master of (un)Stablecoin, Do Kwon. The collection was created to bring everyone back to the good old days when we really thought $UST and $LUNA were going to change the world. Well, on second thought, it did change the world... just in a different way that we'd originally imagined!
